README:
This is a MRI dataset obtained from the offsprings of experimentally induced GDM mothers, consisting of 26 controls and 23 age-matched GDM offsprings of 2-3 months of age. 
This dataset has been converted using BrkRaw (vgd.json) at 2022-05-25 10:14:24.819026. https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3818615.
